Yettem first appeared as a [[census designated place]] in the [[2010 U.S. census]].<ref name=2010CensusCA/> 

The [[2020 United States census]] reported that Yettem had a population of 201. The population density was {{convert|1827|PD/sqmi|PD/km2|sp=us|adj=off}}. The racial makeup of Yettem was 30 (14.9%) [[White Americans|White]], 1 (0.5%) [[African Americans|African American]], 1 (0.5%) [[Native Americans in the United States|Native American]], 3 (1.5%) [[Asian Americans|Asian]], 0 (0.0%) [[Pacific Islander Americans|Pacific Islander]], 123 (61.2%) from [[Race (United States Census)|other races]], and 43 (21.4%) from two or more races. [[Hispanic and Latino Americans|Hispanic or Latino]] of any race were 189 persons (94.0%).<ref name=DP1>{{cite web |title=Yettem CDP, California; DP1: Profile of General Population and Housing Characteristics - 2020 Census of Population and Housing |url=https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALDP2020.DP1?g=160XX00US0686734 |website=US Census Bureau |access-date=May 14, 2025}}</ref>

The census reported that 100% of the population lived in households. There were 49 households, out of which 29 (59%) included children under the age of 18, 26 (53%) were married-couple households, 2 (4%) were [[cohabitation|cohabiting]] couple households, 18 (37%) had a female householder with no partner present, and 3 (6%) had a male householder with no partner present. 2 households (4%) were one person, and 2 (4%) were one person aged 65 or older. The average household size was 4.10.<ref name=DP1/> There were 45 [[family (U.S. Census)|families]] (92% of all households).<ref>{{cite web |title=Yettem CDP, California; P16: Household Type - 2020 Census of Population and Housing |url=https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALDHC2020.P16?g=160XX00US0686734 |website=US Census Bureau |access-date=May 14, 2025}}</ref>

The age distribution was 65 people (32.3%) under the age of 18, 36 people (17.9%) aged 18 to 24, 60 people (29.9%) aged 25 to 44, 27 people (13.4%) aged 45 to 64, and 13 people (6.5%) who were 65{{nbsp}}years of age or older. The median age was 24.9{{nbsp}}years. There were 129 males and 72 females.<ref name=DP1/>

There were 49 housing units at an average density of {{convert|445|/mi2|/km2|disp=preunit|units&nbsp;|units|}}, which were all occupied, 5 (10%) by homeowners, and 44 (90%) by renters.<ref name=DP1/>

